info.author: Domen Kozar
info.description:
.. WARNING::

    Obsolete package You should not use this package any longer. The former django.contrib.localflavor package is now available as the https://pypi.python.org/pypi/django-localflavor package, including the Slovenian localflavor.


Slovenian localflavor for Django
================================

This is the Slovenian localflavor for Django. Currently contained fields are

* SLEMSOField
* SLTaxNumber
* SLPostalCodeField
* SLPhoneNumberField

Source code is very small, read https://github.com/iElectric/django-localflavor-sl/blob/master/localflavor/sl/forms.py


Testing
=======

$ DJANGO_SETTINGS_MODULE="settings" nosetests


Changelog
=========

0.3 (25.12.2010)
----------------

* add SLPhoneNumberField
* renamed EMSOField to SLEMSOField to be more localflavor generic
* renamed SLPostalCodeChoiceField to SLPostalCodeField to be more localflavor generic 
* renamed SLTaxNumber to SLTaxNumberField to be more localflavor generic
* SLTaxNumberField now supports optional SI prefix

0.2 (23.12.2010)
----------------

* Added **SLPostalCodeChoiceField**
* Sorted posts by alphabetic order

0.1 (15.01.2010)
----------------

* Initial release

0.0 (xxxxxxxxxx)
----------------

* forked from hruske
